   Domino effects

   Home Fiches thématiques

   Through the analysis of several singular events, the following fact
   sheet illustrates the dangers associated with some industrial
   activities,  as for example transportation of flammable materials by
   pipelines. Moreover, some dangerous phenomena can be caused by domino
   effects on the surrounding installations. A selection of accidents
   illustrates this last point.

   Date of the document: June 2009
     * Fact sheet : domino effects (FK_imp2009-domino-effects.pdf)

